{"type": "article", "id": 27685, "title": "Jordan 与内马尔签约，以及，刘雯为 Madewell 拍了新广告｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-06-02T10:06:54Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1936, "name": "香水"}, {"id": 757, "name": "巴西"}, {"id": 755, "name": "足球"}, {"id": 3053, "name": "篮球鞋"}, {"id": 23371, "name": "销售额"}, {"id": 28497, "name": "季度增长"}, {"id": 14026, "name": "度假系列"}, {"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 5487, "name": "Jordan"}, {"id": 20675, "name": "Avon"}, {"id": 1653, "name": "Michael Kors"}, {"id": 3111, "name": "Giorgio Armani"}, {"id": 2040, "name": "KENZO"}, {"id": 28498, "name": "Neymar"}, {"id": 129, "name": "Kate Moss"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 46, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702154013STKCbYOyjV7H8xeW.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/Kenzo-to-launch-women-s-fragrance-fashioned-by-its-creative-directors,698341.html#.V05A_IQrJQY\"><b>Kenzo 时装创意总监将发布一款香水</b></a>｜从 2011 年开始执掌 Kenzo 时装、担任创意总监的 Carol Lim 和 Humberto Leon，另一身份是 Opening Ceremony 的创始人。近日这对搭档开始把设计范围拓展到香水，九月将发布一款由他们首次设计的新女士香水。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/giorgio-armani-revenues-growth-10440831/\"><b>阿玛尼宣布 2015 年获增长</b></a>｜Giorgio Armani 近日宣布了 2015 年财政情况，截至 12 月 31 日的 12 个月内，税息折旧及摊销前利润(EBITDA)增长了 1.2% 至 5.13 亿欧元（约合 5.694 亿美元），占销售的 19.4%。由于集团全线品牌及分销渠道的有机增长，收入上涨了 4.5% 至 26.5 亿欧元。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/Avon-appoints-Jack-Stahl-Chairman-of-the-Board-of-Managers,699116.html#.V0-Fj4QrJQY\"><b>雅芳任命新理事会主席</b></a>｜雅芳（Avon）周三宣布 Jack Stahl 担任理事会主席，即刻生效，过去他曾在可口可乐公司担任总裁兼 CEO、露华浓的总裁兼 CEO，有超过 30 年的管理经验。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/Michael-Kors-sales-strongest-sales-in-year-stock-jumps,699114.html#.V0-CR4QrJQY\"><b>Michael Kors 季度销售额大幅增长</b></a>｜Michael Kors 发布截至 4 月 2 日的季度财报，销售额上涨了 10.9% 至 12 亿美元，超出汤森路透 11.5 亿美元的预估。目前世界有 668 家门店，这些门店及线上的销售额上涨了 22%。</p>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p class=\"\">Nike 旗下的<a href=\"http://brandchannel.com/2016/06/01/jordan-brand-neymar-060116/\"> Jordan 品牌与巴西足球明星内马尔（Neymar）签约</a>，这是乔丹品牌首个签约的足球大使，本月将发布 Neymar x Air Jordan 5 Low 鞋款，售价在 200 美元。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153959uxA0cnfZljRYaTsL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.58833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154000UrGz5yvXIVoLjemh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">刘雯为 Madewell 拍摄了新一季牛仔广告：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154000395g0TJZGSavnh4X.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154002JVQlqGuTpZzfHCrk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154003Rtfp4qU3s6CFlB5A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/6/balenciaga-2016-fw-collection\">Balenciaga 发布 2016 年秋冬男装系列：</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154003G9J2zlC7s8BtVRfO.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7559761\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021540046nCUz09tPuMDFrxc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7559761\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154004EdN1ZOx8GsleRFbi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75473579\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021540053BHEGoRAgt4S90zC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7559761\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154005GCpV8Q7hnOFUa1sD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7559761\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154006C2exgI6NEwiRrD7Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7559761\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154006IHW5aUEZADv6Rwg9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7559761\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/runway/resort-2017/milan/giorgio-armani/review/\">Giorgio Armani 2017 度假系列</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154007UKagAJYzNwx9qhVn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154007Fznm1gB7KkISbDP5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75092593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/media-news/fashion-memopad/kate-moss-alberta-ferretti-ads-fall-10440002/\">Alberta Ferretti 找来 Kate Moss 拍摄秋季广告</a>：<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154007xDeAfdX23v4cBOuE.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154008QO9T3Ccl705s8Nb4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">日本设计师<a href=\"http://popbee.com/lifestyle/home-and-living/haruka-misawa/\">三则遥（Haruka Misawa）设计了十来款创意鱼缸</a>，从自然界中汲取灵感：</p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154009HdnYtS6J3Tz0FvVa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702